item.dc:creator: @skeebo skeebo
item.description:
@skeebo wrote:

look on your router ( i have verizon too and i can port forward)

you should see one of the following:

E90-610014-06
E90-610015-06
E90-610030-06

if not, let me know.

if you have E90-610014-06 go to this link
http://www.portforward.com/english/routers/port_forwarding/Westell/E90-610014-06/default.htm

if you have E90-610015-06 go to this link
http://www.portforward.com/english/routers/port_forwarding/Westell/E90-610015-06/default.htm

if you have E90-610030-06 go to this link
http://www.portforward.com/english/routers/port_forwarding/Westell/E90-610030-06/default.htm

just follow what it says, it’s a step-by-step guide.

if you need any help let me know
